<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sacred-adj">sacred <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'seɪkrɪd/    美 /'seɪkrɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>神圣的；宗教 (性) 的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the sacred Olympic flame 
奥运圣火</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Temples and churches are all sacred buildings. 
寺庙和教堂都是宗教建筑。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>郑重的；庄严的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a sacred promise 
郑重的承诺</p></div></div>